《'''悬战'''》（{{lang-en|''War on a String''}}）是中国大陆黑色[[悬疑片|悬疑]][[犯罪片|犯罪片]]，导演和编剧都是李凯，主演焦恩俊、连凯、林津锋、韩秋池、彭博、高菲、戚云鹏、胡双泉。<ref>{{cite news |author= |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2015-04-09/doc-iawzuney2870259.shtml |title=《悬战》概念海报定档5.8 焦恩俊命悬一线 |newspaper=新浪网 |access-date=2015-05-10 |date=2015-04-09 |archive-date=2019-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191003184656/http://ent.sina.com.cn/m/c/2015-04-09/doc-iawzuney2870259.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author= |url=http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/hqcj/xfly/2015-05-01/content_13634985.html |title=《悬战》终极海报 焦恩俊内心戏重 |newspaper=中国日报 |date=2015-05-01 |access-date=2015-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304192110/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/hqcj/xfly/2015-05-01/content_13634985.html |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==剧情==
该片讲述黑社会李鸿声等人和警察王维之间的生死搏斗。

